# GeoLite2 mmdb files (GeoLite2-ASN.mmdb, GeoLite2-City.mmdb) are excluded from
# this public mirror per MaxMind's EULA. The Dockerfile COPY of this directory
# still succeeds (empty dir is valid), and the gateway boots without them —
# the GeoMap dashboard degrades gracefully. Populate at runtime by either:
#   • dropping fresh mmdbs into the /data volume, or
#   • setting MAXMIND_LICENSE_KEY so the container auto-refreshes on start.
